title: Dog rescued from River Ouzel in Walton Hall near Milton Keynes after becoming stuck
content: Plans for a new supermarket in Olney, which were withdrawn following a backlash about proposed housing on a site allocated for retail use only, have been re-submitted with the supermarket remaining the same size as proposed when housing was to be included.
